data.description: Come see this spacious single family home in the sought after community of Summerville in Homestead. This home features a split floor plan with 4 ample bedrooms and 3 bathrooms (1 bedroom and 1 bathroom downstairs), 2 car garage, a massive chef's kitchen with beautiful wood cabinetry, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, combination tile and carpet flooring throughout, tall volume ceilings, tons of closet space, laundry room conveniently located upstairs and so much more. Outdoors, enjoy a welcoming, fully fenced in private patio with enough room for a pool and space for entertainment.  Low HOA fees! Close to major highways, shopping and dining.
